@startuml
title Transaction Service - Startup Flow

participant "Transaction Service" as MS
participant "Config Server" as CS
participant "Eureka Server" as EU

MS -> CS : Load configuration (optional)
CS --> MS : application.yml properties

MS -> EU : Register service (TRANSACTION-SERVICE)
EU --> MS : Registered instance

note right of MS
Service ready:
- API Gateway routing active
- MongoDB connection ready
- RxJava reactive endpoints enabled
end note

@enduml